It ought to be a hot spot, that tavern ...
The brew's rich and strong;
bright pennants fly above to brag
that they offer full measure.
So how come they're not selling?
The joint is full of grinning dogs.
A kid comes in to grab a drink ...
Dogs growlï¼š he's gone.
